StoreMate-parent 1.0.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
com.fasterxml.storemate.backend.bdbje
Package that contains main BDB-JE back-end implementation.
com.fasterxml.storemate.backend.bdbje.util
Package that contains miscellaneous utility methods used by BDB-JE backend implementation.
com.fasterxml.storemate.backend.leveldb
Package that contains main LevelDB (java) back-end implementation.
com.fasterxml.storemate.shared
Package that contains datatypes and utilities needed by storemate store and core client functionality.
com.fasterxml.storemate.shared.compress
Package that contains convenience access to standard compression algorithsm (GZIP, LZF) that StoreMate supports.
com.fasterxml.storemate.shared.hash
Package that contains core hashing interfaces and implementations of StoreMate.
com.fasterxml.storemate.shared.util
Package that contains miscellaneous utility methods used by StoreMate classes.
com.fasterxml.storemate.store  
com.fasterxml.storemate.store.backend
Package that contains abstractions used by frontend to access storage-system dependant backend implementations.
com.fasterxml.storemate.store.file
Package that contains implementations of disk-backed BLOB storage including handling of directory structure needed to store BLOBs using somewhat balanced directory structures.
com.fasterxml.storemate.store.impl  
com.fasterxml.storemate.store.lastaccess
Package that contains interface used by optional last-accessed data stores; not all systems use this, but all backends need to implement such storage.
com.fasterxml.storemate.store.state
Package that contains abstractions needed for storing local node state information; metadata about system that runs using StoreMate, not actual data stored (or metadata thereof).
com.fasterxml.storemate.store.util
